        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "My Serverprovider hasn't set the Variables used in Zend_Cache_Backend->getTmpDir() so the returned value is '\/tmp'. This directory isn't writeable an so i get Errors -- i don't even use Zend_Cache, just wanted to use Zend_Date.\n\nAs a quickfix i added $_ENV['TMPDIR'] = session_save_path() but i think this should be fixed in Zend_Cache_Backend.\nProbably it could be tested if \/tmp is writeable and if not use session_save_path? I don't know..."
        },
