                    "body": "just commited something better into SVN trunk\n\ncan you try it ?\n\n(you have only to take the Backend.php file from SVN trunk)",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=fab",
